description.en:
It is implemented in AOK blockchain platform - AOK Mainnet, which is released. In the years since the white paper was released and the mainnet launched, the speed and quality of the AOK blockchain shows the performance of many applications operating normally, and the blockchain network is operating soundly.
 
With the recent rapid spread of infectious diseases, utilizing the AOK network with proven speed, functionality, and diverse applications for rapid deployment and effective service introduction of MEC-Chain will focus on the rapid development of MEC Test Service and active participation of Test Kit manufacturers and Test Service agencies as well as the flexibility and ease of users' test service infrastructure.
